  m_Name: Dlg_Ruins_Totem_Aether
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Ancient Totem
  _lines:
  - The totem's hollow eyes seem to track you. A dry whisper rises from the stone.
  - Take the living spark of essence and give it wholly to the open air. What remains is the pure breath of the heavens.
